PrecisAppointment of DANIEL CHARBONNEAU, of Roxboro, Quebec, as a member of the Canada Industrial Relaltions Board, to hold office during good behaviour for a term of three years, effective March 29, 1999; and order that DANIEL CHARBONNEAU be deemed to be employed in the Public Service for the purposes of the Public Service Superannuation Act.

precis:
Appointment of DANIEL CHARBONNEAU, of Roxboro, Quebec, as a member of the
Canada Industrial Relaltions Board, to hold office during good behaviour
for a term of three years, effective March 29, 1999; and order that
DANIEL CHARBONNEAU be deemed to be employed in the Public Service for the
purposes of the Public Service Superannuation Act.
